nomenclaturalStatus: Basionym ref as ' Gymnocalycium 16(3): 529 (2003)', appears to be correctible typographical error, as the text immediately preceding states 'in 2004, Till & Amerhauser described plants from the Tucabaca valley as  G. anisitsii subsp. holdii var. tucavocense', which is given in the references as Gymnocalycium 17(1). The 2003 citation has var. griseopallidum, but not var. tucavocense.
